## Also check these two things:

1. **Vercel Deployment Protection must be OFF** — Go to your Vercel dashboard → your project → **Settings → Deployment Protection** → toggle off "Vercel Authentication". This is almost certainly why it can't find your manifest even if the file exists.

2. **Test the manifest URL directly** — Open this in your browser:
   https://base-nexus.vercel.app/.well-known/farcaster.json
